title: Put Up Your Dukes
description: The Duke visit their Australian cousin Willy in Kingsburry who's planning to get rich by having his kangaroo Bouncing Benny become a boxing champion.

title: Jungle Jitters
description: The Dukes are forced to take a short cut through the unexplored South American jungle. But they are captured by a native tribe and the General Lee about to be sacrificed to a volcano.

title: The Greece Fleece
description: Boss Hogg makes sure his friend Big Nic Metropopolus arrests the Dukes and throws them in jail. He then attends the local Aphrodite festival and ends up having to marry Nic's niece Melina.

title: The Dukes in Urbekistan
description: Racing through Ubreksitan, the Dukes meet British Debra Far, who is looking for her Geologist father. Boss becomes interested when he learns Professor Far was searching for a diamond mine.

title: The Dukes in Hong Kong
description: Boss makes the Dukes believe he's out of the race, while in reality he's converted his caddy into a hydrofoil and takes a short cut over the water. But when Hogg strikes a deal with Captain Crikey of the pirate ship Sea Scum, both he and the Dukes end up in trouble.

title: The Dukes Do Paris
description: Boss Hogg is meeting the criminal Blankie LeBlanc in France to get his hands on a valuable Blue Oiseau stamp. But Le Blanc accidentally gives the stamp to Daisy who is about to send a postcard to Uncle Jessie.

title: The Dukes in Switzerland
description: Racing through Switzerland, the Dukes pick up a girl called Lilly who is on the run from the Slavonian secret police. The spies are after her father's secret formula.

title: Boss O'Hogg and the Little People
description: When Boss Hogg and Rosco capture a Leprechaun and force him to give him not just his own pot of gold but those of his friends as well, the Grand Wizard of the Leprechauns puts him on trial. It's up to the Dukes to safe the Hogg.

title: Tales of the Vienna Hoods
description: Boss is babysitting his ten year old niece Cindy Sue while her parents are on a skiing trip. Since the honest little girl won't allow for him to do nothing crooked, Boss asks the Dukes for a 'truce' and dumps the little girl on them while goes to do some business in Viena.

title: The Kid from Madrid
description: The Dukes meet young Peppino and his racing horse El Blanco while driving through Spain. Boss Hogg is in league with a rival horse racer, Señor Geraldo, owner of the competing horse El Diablo, who asks him to kidnap El Blanco.

title: The Canadian Caper
description: The Dukes get car trouble in Canada and help young Suzette LeFite bust the fur poaching brothers Pierre et Louis Bouchard (who just happen to doing business with Boss Hogg).

title: The Dukes in Hollywood
description: The Dukes become Hollywood stunt drivers for child star Roddy Cooper latest film. Boss Hogg is soon talked into taking being the executive producer.

title: A Hogg in the Foggy Bogg
description: Uncle Jesse finds old Great-Uncle Cyrus Duke's treasure map and heads to the Philipines where his Cousins are racing, to find Cyrus' treasure. However it is hidden in a swamp that is supposed to be haunted by a hairy monster.
